<h2>Reporting new bugs</h2>

<p>
  If the GUI is crashing then before filing a bug report, collect
  basic debugging information using the <code>--debug-entangle</code>
  command line flag
</p>

<p>
  If a camera is not behaving well with Entangle, then before filing
  a bug report, collect gphoto2 debugging information using the
  <code>--debug-gphoto</code> command line flag
</p>

[% END %]
